MO OS update trust store

The production public key must be installed as:

  /etc/mo/trust/update-public.pem

No private signing key may be stored in the ISO, repository, installed root,
CI artifacts, or update bundle. Alpha 0.5 CI generates a temporary key pair,
uses only its public half for verification, and destroys both when the job ends.

A production key will be enrolled only after offline custody, rotation and
revocation procedures are defined and tested.
